  "3035140": {
    "name": "WonderLang French",
    "steam_appid": 3035140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>WonderLang French</strong>，在这里，学习法语会变成一场<strong>引人入胜的 RPG 冒险旅程</strong>。通过精彩的任务、互动对话和有趣的谜题，<strong>让语言学习变得自然又轻松、有趣</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本页面介绍的是 WonderLang 的<strong>法语学习版本</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可从以下基础语言学习法语：英语、法语、西班牙语、德语、意大利语、葡萄牙语、韩语、中文、日语、荷兰语、印尼语、波兰语、俄语、乌克兰语和阿拉伯语。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WonderLang 还提供其他版本，帮助你学习<strong>法语、西班牙语、德语、葡萄牙语、意大利语、韩语和日语</strong>。<strong>中文版本预计将在 2025 年 12 月上线</strong>，<strong>英语版本将在 2026 年 1 月推出</strong>。另外还有 <strong>WonderLang Polyglot</strong> 版本，只需一次购买，就能解锁<strong>当前和未来的所有语言</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无需安装，直接在浏览器中试玩 Demo：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WonderLang 将语言学习深度融入冒险与故事之中。在游戏中，你会通过<strong>探索</strong>、<strong>战斗</strong>、<strong>对话</strong>和<strong>调查</strong>来使用你的<strong>目标语言</strong>，让每一个任务和互动都成为真正的练习机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>比任何订阅制语言学习应用都更实惠、更有沉浸感、也更好玩。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/54ca8ef42134991cf18b18b054ee353d.avif?t=1765894484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras_big/54ca8ef42134991cf18b18b054ee353d.avif?t=1765894484 width=800 height=221 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WonderLang 专为<strong>语言初学者</strong>设计，即使完全没有法语基础，也可以直接进入游戏。从头到尾，游戏并不是为了完全取代传统课程，而是为你提供一个<strong>沉浸式、愉快的环境</strong>，让你在游玩过程中逐步练习一门新语言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式法语学习</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一段对话、每一个任务和谜题中学习实用法语。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供<strong>超过 45 小时</strong>的游戏与学习内容。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置<strong>3 种模式</strong>，可根据需要调整难度，适合<strong>零基础、A1 和 A2 水平</strong>的学习者。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/75d0459a948d54e66fb02c8ff1cc257c.apng?t=1765894484\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/75d0459a948d54e66fb02c8ff1cc257c.poster.avif?t=1765894484\" class=\"bb_img\" width=73 height=107 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜的剧情</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随一位年轻主角的旅程，他必须学会法语，才能解除降临在哥哥身上的魔法诅咒。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充满生机的村庄，发现隐藏的秘密，并与超过<strong>60 个独特 NPC</strong>建立友谊。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/91eb45cdbf2905c57aea71a7aea529e5.avif?t=1765894484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras_big/91eb45cdbf2905c57aea71a7aea529e5.avif?t=1765894484 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏玩法即学习过程</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过造句和理解对话来解开谜题、完成任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用<strong>语音识别挑战</strong>来练习句子表达和发音。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用游戏中的<strong>词典</strong>和<strong>上下文提示</strong>来帮助理解和学习。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                                                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/6e46f68cb2492ee721f0862c735137dd.poster.avif?t=1765894484\" width=74 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/6e46f68cb2492ee721f0862c735137dd.webm?t=1765894484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于间隔重复的战斗挑战</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与<strong>以语言为核心的战斗</strong>，反复巩固词汇与语法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗挑战基于<strong>间隔重复（spaced repetition）原理</strong>设计，有助于形成长期记忆。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/d7f61f1bd28f1c79136bfcafa8dd3171.avif?t=1765894484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras_big/d7f61f1bd28f1c79136bfcafa8dd3171.avif?t=1765894484 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>贴近生活的实用练习</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>日常场景</strong>中运用法语，比如买东西、看医生预约等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>接近真实生活的语境</strong>中体验实用词汇和语法，提升自信与表达能力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                                                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/b9e13f2969f444e4174b8735c86f02fc.poster.avif?t=1765894484\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/b9e13f2969f444e4174b8735c86f02fc.webm?t=1765894484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可自定义的学习体验</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过难度设置，让你的冒险更轻松或更有挑战性，自由调整学习节奏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设定<strong>每日目标</strong>并完成后获取奖励，帮助你养成持续学习的习惯。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/388a122f3327cf08ed38a6e3c25051df.avif?t=1765894484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras_big/388a122f3327cf08ed38a6e3c25051df.avif?t=1765894484 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富而互动的世界</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索各种风格各异的地点</strong>，每个地点都会引入与之相关的法语词汇和语法结构。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验<strong>小游戏</strong>，例如填字游戏、记忆游戏和比划猜词等，让学习方式更加多样化。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/347390bf861aacbbd7ee3836ea784c98.avif?t=1765894484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras_big/347390bf861aacbbd7ee3836ea784c98.avif?t=1765894484 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你可以使用键盘和鼠标、仅鼠标或仅键盘来游玩 WonderLang。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏也在 Steam Deck 上有出色表现，并提供官方按键布局。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无需安装，直接在浏览器中试玩 Demo：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/ccdf73f1ea974747a06efb92cb695755.apng?t=1765894484\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/ccdf73f1ea974747a06efb92cb695755.poster.avif?t=1765894484\" class=\"bb_img\" width=89 height=90 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/939ca7fb7c6ef58353da17d0ff77dd07.apng?t=1765894484\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035140/extras/939ca7fb7c6ef58353da17d0ff77dd07.poster.avif?t=1765894484\" class=\"bb_img\" width=100 height=98 /></picture></span></p>",
